 Stereophonics 的 Kelly Jones 猛烈抨击人工智能在歌曲创作中的使用https://www.nme.com/news/music/stereophonics-kelly-jones-hits-out-at-use-of-ai-in-songwriting-3473528?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=stereophonics-kelly-jones-在歌曲创作中使用人工智能的热门歌曲Hollie GeraghtyWed, 26 Jul 2023 06:43:02 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3473528 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我认为艺术一直是某个人的表达，一个真实的人发自内心、来自头脑的表达”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stereophonics-kelly-jones-hits-out-at-use-of-ai-in-songwriting-3473528">Stereophonics 的 Kelly Jones 抨击在歌曲创作中使用人工智能的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/kelly-jones-stereophonics-ai-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stereophonics">立体声</a>主唱凯利·琼斯批评了在歌曲创作中使用人工智能。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/stereophonics-kelly-jones-interview-oochya-right-place-right-time-3163921">我们从与 Stereophonics 的 Kelly Jones 的对话视频聊天中了解到的五件事</a></strong></li></ul><p>随着越来越多的艺术家公开谈论人工智能在音乐行业的日益普及，这位歌手表示艺术是“真实的人的表达”。</p><p>周日（7 月 23 日），琼斯在 Latitude Festival 上与新乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/far-from-saints">Far From Saints</a>一起演出后，在接受<em>Times Radio</em>采访时分享了他对人工智能的怀疑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3386626" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3386626" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3386626" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/KellyJones-Stereophonics-Far-From-Saints.jpg" alt="远离圣徒新闻照片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/KellyJones-Stereophonics-Far-From-Saints.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/KellyJones-Stereophonics-Far-From-Saints-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/KellyJones-Stereophonics-Far-From-Saints-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/KellyJones-Stereophonics-Far-From-Saints-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/KellyJones-Stereophonics-Far-From-Saints-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/KellyJones-Stereophonics-Far-From-Saints-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3386626" class="wp-caption-text">远离圣人。图片来源：索菲亚·法兰西</figcaption></figure><p>这位音乐家表示，直到今年 5 月参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/harry-styles-wet-leg-raye-and-more-win-at-2023-ivor-novello-awards-3445689">艾弗·诺韦洛奖 (Ivor Novello Awards) 时</a>，他才透露人工智能技术正被更多地用于“完成人们的歌曲创作”（来自<em><a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/ce9g30jvm5qo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC</a></em> ）。</p><p> “我并不反对前瞻性技术以及事物的进展方式，但我认为艺术应该来自于人，无论如何我指的是它的基础知识，”他说。</p><p> “我认为艺术一直是某个人的表达，一个真实的人发自内心、来自头脑的表达。”</p><p>他补充道：“如果你要开始一个想法，那么计算机就会完成它，我的意思是，这没关系，但这只是关于算法和类似的事情。”</p><p>这位歌手还表示，他“不太喜欢一首歌有 10 名词曲作者”，并补充道：“这就像你在画一幅画，有 10 个画家在画布上涂颜料。我是说，这是谁的画？”</p><p>琼斯并不是第一个对音乐行业新兴人工智能技术表示怀疑的艺术家。今年早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-calls-chatgpt-and-ai-songwriting-a-grotesque-mockery-of-what-it-is-to-be-human-3381620">Nick Cave 称 ChatGPT 和人工智能歌曲创作是“对人类的怪诞嘲讽”</a> 。</p><p>最近，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">斯汀</a>表示人工智能“没有给他留下深刻的印象”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sting-says-songwriting-battle-between-humans-and-ai-is-coming-3445016">歌曲作者必须捍卫“我们的人力资本免受人工智能的侵害”</a> 。然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/smashing-pumpkins">Smashing Pumpkins</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">Billy Corgan</a>表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/smashing-pumpkins-billy-corgan-says-ai-will-change-music-forever-3446083">“人工智能将永远改变音乐”，</a>因为其他人可以“玩弄系统”并且“不会在地下室度过 10,000 个小时”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3449695" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3449695" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3449695" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Nick-Cave-Posing.jpg" alt="尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave) 出席 2017 年 7 月 26 日在加利福尼亚州洛杉矶艾斯酒店剧院举行的《风河》首映式。图片来源：Jason LaVeris / GETTY" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Nick-Cave-Posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Nick-Cave-Posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Nick-Cave-Posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Nick-